<div id="about" class="panel" title="Mobile Banking">
  <h2>Available to all Online Banking customers. With Mobile Banking you can use your iPhone or iPod touch to easily and securely check your balance and pay your bills.  Itâ€™s fast, easy and convenient - just use the Safari browser on your iPhone or iPod touch to get started.</h2>
